# Minimal C++17 Interaction (POC idea)

Here’s a simplified flow:

while (true) {
    MarketData md = feed.read();

    strategy.onMarketData(md);

    if (strategy.hasOrder()) {
        Order o = strategy.getOrder();
        gateway.send(o);
    }

    ExecutionReport er;
    if (gateway.receive(er)) {
        strategy.onExecution(er);
    }
}

